sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant B as Browser
    participant S as Streamlit
    participant SX as StreamTeX

    U->>B: Open app
    B->>S: HTTP request
    S->>SX: st_book(blocks)
    SX->>SX: Load TOC + Markers
    SX->>S: Render HTML
    S->>B: Response
    B->>U: Display page
    U->>B: Navigate (PageDown)
    B->>S: Rerun
    S->>SX: Render next block
    SX->>S: HTML fragment
    S->>B: Updated page
